Project Description

This project focuses on analyzing customer demographic and income data using advanced Excel features. The dataset includes information related to customer age groups, occupation, salary, marital status, and family size. The analysis was performed using advanced formulas, Pivot Tables, Pivot Charts, and interactive dashboards to uncover trends and patterns in customer demographics and earnings.

The project demonstrates proficiency in:

Advanced Excel formulas
Data cleaning and transformation
Pivot Tables and Pivot Charts
Interactive dashboard creation
Demographic and salary analysis
Data visualization and reporting
